N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 361.6 - Obligations

State Regulations

The obligations of a self-insurer shall include all its
obligations, and those of each and every employer for whose employees the
self-insurer provides benefits under section
211
of the Workers' Compensation Law. Notes
